 ### Priority 2 — Later Region Encounters
 
-These can use a generic placeholder until custom sprites are created. Use `incident_placeholder.png` as the `spriteKey` fallback.
+These ship without a sprite until custom art is created. Do **not** set a placeholder `spriteKey` — leave the field absent so the game no-ops cleanly rather than attempting to load a non-existent fallback image.
 
 | Incident ID | Visual Concept |
 |---|---|
